Emulators used:
	* NES-CHIP-8 by NovaSquirrel https://github.com/NovaSquirrel/NES-CHIP-8
	  zlib License with modifications by sirfredrick
	* PocketNES originally by loopy and flubba
	  https://web.archive.org/web/20120427045643/http://www.pocketnes.org/
	  Public Domain with miniLZO under GPLv2 or later
	  used with modifications by catskull https://github.com/catskull/pocketnes
	* VBA GX by Tantric and contributors
	  https://github.com/dborth/vbagx GPLv2 (updated due to clarification by
	  developer)
	* Dolphin Emulator by many contributors
	  https://github.com/dolphin-emu/dolphin GPLv2 or later

